text:
A guide to copyright law as it applies to music. Prepared by the Music Publishers Association. Includes information such as: Permission Forms & Informational PDFs; Frequently Asked Copyright Questions; Streaming Live Music: What You Need To Know; Distance Learning and Using Copyrighted Music; Creating Authorized Orchestral Pops Arrangements;
Creating Authorized Band Arrangements; Creating Authorized Choir Arrangements;
Quick Guide to Copyright; Copying Under Copyright; Resources for Churches
